TI  - Neurophilic Biomimetic Lipoprotein-Mediated Targeted Nerve Growth Factor Delivery for Traumatic Brain Injury Therapy
PY  - 2025
T2  - Advanced Science
VL  - 12
IS  - 42
C7  - e09405
