TI  - Multifunctional Fluoropolymer-Engineered Magnetic Nanoparticles to Facilitate Blood-Brain Barrier Penetration and Effective Gene Silencing in Medulloblastoma
PY  - 2024
T2  - Advanced Science
VL  - 11
IS  - 25
C7  - 2401340
