TI  - Amelioration of Post-Stroke Edema and Microcirculatory Dysfunction via Targeted AQP4 Inhibition While Preserving the Glymphatic System
PY  - 2026
T2  - Advanced Science
VL  - 13
IS  - 10
C7  - e20118
